Glitch Effect: 

Use the following link to get the shader file and texture
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1GcJpC6KdB9uerL75z4Obz6DStBsCtUFH
Import the files into Unity
Create a new material and assign the custom shader.
Add the texture and customize as required.

Glow Effect:

Shader with Emission emission color (not black ) intensity > 0
Post Processing Bloom Intesnity and threshold
Render Pipleine Assert enable HDR
Camera - Enable post processing
